{"tid":1697412,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港大深圳醫院醫生疑預簽收據　港大醫療系統稱完成調查","createTime":"2019-11-07T00:17:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T00:49:50.000Z","uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"39bb13d3c48e18197bd3cfe4c965aff3f7dc2ad7","tid":1697412,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T00:17:29.000Z","msg":"牛頭角淘大商場在9月，發生不同政見人士打鬥事件，現場遺下幾張由一名港大深圳醫院醫生預先簽發的收據，涉事醫生被暫停職務。<br />\n<br />\n港大醫療系統表示，事件的獨立調查委員會，上星期完成調查工作，報告已呈交大學管理層。<br />\n<br />\n發言人說，校方會在完成審閱報告内容及調查結果後，啟動進一步人事紀律程序和作出處置，目前有關人士的臨床職務仍然暫停，只被安排執行文書工作。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1490482-20191106.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1490482-20191106.htm&d=40Eeu%2FLL1847%2FNonScroNQpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=33550add\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1490482-20191106.htm&h=53889096\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1490482-20191106.htm</a>"},{"pid":"b5aaef6b323cf91f0c064708b8357f0f8436904a","tid":1697412,"uid":13474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T00:18:38.000Z","msg":"[重新整合]11.10 7區開花！ 11.11全港3罷！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1697199\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1697199</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a0f2530c2f76979a5cc601c577c869e84f231b9a","tid":1697412,"uid":82532,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T00:32:53.000Z","msg":"口頭警告算"},{"pid":"0a2d5e40d2d4233e57182aceee6a0221f9a1a1f6","tid":1697412,"uid":102078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0f2530c2f76979a5cc601c577c869e84f231b9a","tid":1697412,"uid":82532,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T00:32:53.000Z","msg":"口頭警告算"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T00:34:40.000Z","msg":"Yes,繼續馬照跑 舞照跳"},{"pid":"b9048c59cb87d0ee7a8dff83762d1763b6ece9